title: BEGIN_SCALEFORM_MOVIE_METHOD_ON_FRONTEND_HEADER
content:
0xB9449845F73F5E9C0x5E219B67// BeginScaleformMovieMethodOnFrontendHeader
BOOL BEGIN_SCALEFORM_MOVIE_METHOD_ON_FRONTEND_HEADER(char* functionName);Parameters:functionName: Scaleform function name.Starts frontend (pause menu) scaleform movie methods for header options.Use BEGIN_SCALEFORM_MOVIE_METHOD_ON_FRONTEND to customize the content inside the frontend menus.Old name:  _BEGIN_SCALEFORM_MOVIE_METHOD_V
